reviewText: For any American Dad lovers,  you must have these seasons.  Kinda bummed they haven't made the new seasons and season ten was official but one of those manufacturer dvds.
this show is funny and excellent i can't stop watching it all the time it beats out all those other shows

I had been looking to establish my collection of this hilarious series and, after comparing prices, I hooked up with this amazing set for an outstanding price. Once again, thanks Amazon for having the best of it all!
My family loves American Dad , so when I saw all the seasons together I had to buy it and the price was a perfect ,thank you for the great service
